title: ABC News' Jonathan Karl unpacks Trump's behavior this week
description: NPR's Steve Inskeep looks back at President Trump's behavior over the past week with Jonathan Karl of ABC News. He's the author of "Retribution: Donald Trump and the Campaign That Changed America."
